34char *
35dwarf_find_macro_value_start(char *macro_string)
36{
37 char *p;
38
39 if (macro_string == NULL)
40 return (NULL);
41
42 p = macro_string;
43 while (*p != '\0' && *p != ' ')
44 p++;
45 if (*p == ' ')
46 p++;
47
48 return (p);
49}

51int
52dwarf_get_macro_details(Dwarf_Debug dbg, Dwarf_Off offset,
53 Dwarf_Unsigned max_count, Dwarf_Signed *entry_cnt,
54 Dwarf_Macro_Details **details, Dwarf_Error *error)
55{
56 Dwarf_MacroSet ms;
57 Dwarf_Unsigned cnt;
58 int i;
59
60 if (dbg == NULL || entry_cnt == NULL || details == NULL) {
61 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
62 return (DW_DLV_ERROR);
63 }
64
65 if (STAILQ_EMPTY(&dbg->dbg_mslist)) {
66 if (_dwarf_macinfo_init(dbg, error) != DW_DLE_NONE)
67 return (DW_DLV_ERROR);
68 if (STAILQ_EMPTY(&dbg->dbg_mslist)) {
69 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_NO_ENTRY);
70 return (DW_DLV_NO_ENTRY);
71 }
72 }
73
74 STAILQ_FOREACH(ms, &dbg->dbg_mslist, ms_next) {
75 for (i = 0; (Dwarf_Unsigned) i < ms->ms_cnt; i++)
76 if (ms->ms_mdlist[i].dmd_offset == offset) {
77 cnt = ms->ms_cnt - i;
78 if (max_count != 0 && cnt > max_count)
79 cnt = max_count;
80
81 *details = &ms->ms_mdlist[i];
82 *entry_cnt = cnt;
83
84 return (DW_DLV_OK);
85 }
86 }
87
88 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_NO_ENTRY);
89
90 return (DW_DLV_NO_ENTRY);
91}
